{
  "id": "adv_main_01_07_04",
  "title": "星見編2章24話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.06666666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "なあ、すず\nやっぱりちゃんとご両親と話し合わないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen‚ Suzu.\nWon’t you reconsider talking this over with your parents?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4000000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……無理ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "事務所としてもご両親から許可がもらえない限り\n継続することはできないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But as long as you’re in our agency without your parents’ permission‚\nwe can’t keep you here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……！！\nいえ、星見プロがダメなら、他の事務所でも……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…!\nI mean‚ if Hoshimi Productions won’t have me‚ then I’ll join another agency!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.200000000000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、他の事務所でも無理だよ\nそれでOKなんて事務所、真っ当なところじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ other agencies wouldn’t take you.\nAnd if it’s an agency that will accept you without parental consent‚ it’s shady.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.31689585214374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.129704146697755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ご両親との話し合いをそこまで嫌がるのはどうしてだ？\n自分の意志を否定されたから、ってだけじゃないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so adamantly against talking this over with your parents?\nIt can’t be just because they rejected your wishes‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.52970414669776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "……アイドルになる、という私の意志を否定されたのは\n事実です。そしてお母様達は言いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is true that they rejected my wish to become an idol.\nThis is what my parents said:",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.39637081336442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "蝶よ花よと甘やかしてしまったから\nすずはすっかり世間を知らない子に育ってしまった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Because we spoiled you‚ calling you a butterfly and a flower‚\nyou’ve grown up into a very sheltered‚ ignorant girl.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.04637071799697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ここは心を鬼にして、すずに一人でアメリカ留学を\nしてもらおうと思っている、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“You need tough love. We’re thinking of\nsending you to America alone to study.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.34637071799698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "ですから私……\n家を飛び出してきてしまったのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that’s why\nI ran away from home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.329804882769416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（すずが甘やかされてきたのはわかる）\n（ご両親も後悔したうえでの判断なんだろうな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It’s obvious that Suzu was coddled.)\n(Her parents probably made that decision out of regret.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.70212341415871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 64.93545674749204
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "でも誤解なさらないでください。アイドルは私の夢\n留学したくないから目指す訳ではありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But please don’t misunderstand me. Becoming an idol is my dream.\nI’m not trying to be an idol just because I don’t want to move to America.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.70212341415869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "私は長瀬麻奈様のいた星見プロで、アイドルになりたい\n――そうずっと、強く願っていたのですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to become an idol at Hoshimi Productions‚ where Goddess Mana was.\nI’ve wished for that for a very long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.03545674749203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "……かつて麻奈様もおっしゃっていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Goddess Mana once said something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.33838173019873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "どんな困難が立ち塞がっても、自分を信じて突き進めば\nきっと打ち破れる、と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“No matter what obstacles block your path‚ if you believe in yourself and push through‚\nyou can break through anything.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "あの麻奈様のお言葉がなければ、私は星見プロの前で\n二の足を踏んでいたかもしれません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Goddess Mana hadn’t said that‚ I might have had second thoughts\nabout joining Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.83806744228647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なあ、すずはどうしてアイドルになりたいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell me‚ Suzu‚ why do you want to be an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.20473410895316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのマネージャーたる者が何を言いますか！\n麻奈様を見た女子がアイドルに憧れるのは、当然のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re a Hoshimi Productions manager! How can you even ask that?\nEvery girl who has seen Goddess Mana dreams of becoming an idol! It’s only natural!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.69870232553126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、そうですわね\nかつて私が麻奈様の言葉に背中を押してもらったように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But yes‚ there is another reason.\nGoddess Mana’s words gave me the push I needed in the past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.27584532708772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "私もまた、夢を抱いた人の背中を押してあげられる\n存在になりたい、とも思っていますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I want to be someone who can give another dreamer the push she needs.\nThat’s the kind of person I want to be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.82711511265094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "私の言葉が、すずちゃんの背中を押してたなんて\n……はは、ちょっと照れちゃうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t believe my words inspired Suzu that much.\nHaha. She’s making me blush.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.16044844598431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それだけの熱意があるなら、やっぱり\nちゃんと話し合うべきじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re really that passionate about it‚\nthen don’t you think you should talk it over with your parents?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2104484459846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 136.74378177931777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "……何度も話し合いましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We did talk it over many times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.2771151126513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "でもお母様達は、自分達の考えが正しいと信じて\n疑わないのです。私の話なんて、聞いてくれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But my parents are convinced they’re in the right‚\nand they can’t be shaken. They’ll never hear me out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.42135543635385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ。すずちゃんって、本当は\nお母さん達のことが大好きなんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ I think that Suzu actually\nloves her parents very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.25468876968714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、話し合いになったら相手の話を聞いちゃって\n自分の気持ちを伝えきれない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So if she tries to talk to them‚ she’ll just wind up listening to them too much\nand she won’t be able to communicate her own feelings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.65468876968706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ち、私には分かる気がする\nでも、それじゃ前に進めないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I understand that feeling.\nBut she’ll never make any progress like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.6213554363538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……すずのお母さんは\nすずがアイドルになるのは無理だって言うんだよ",
